				\begin{document}$${\rm{\Pr }}(\frac{|{\rm{\Delta }}T|}{\overline{|{\rm{\Delta }}T|}} > s)$$\end{document}Pr(|ΔT||ΔT|¯>s) is the probability that a randomly chosen spike \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
