Gaussian series are not intermittent since c(γ) = 0 for all the spikes. To see this, note that for Gaussian processes the cumulative probability of a spike exceeding a fixed threshold s is independent of the resolution λ, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
